{"tid":1503151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我們應集中「三大核彈」可影響世界達50年","createTime":"2019-08-25T00:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T02:23:37.000Z","uid":266362,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"830ab52dc83d6afe2dee4c3c3d27a78a22718775","tid":1503151,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T00:16:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">非常重要！香港將影響全世界50年發展</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人集中「三大核彈」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">(1) 首先便是香港國際機場</span>，因香港機場擁有世界第一的物流轉運港，世界貨運量第一，客運量也達世界第三，當中涉及既合約、保險、金額之巨，一旦停滯，為世界帶來的經濟損失將是天文數字。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">(2) 第二，港人應向世界宣揚中共惡行</span>，並共同制止中共行惡。上述前白宮幕僚長班農（Steve Bannon）在8月22日的訪談中也多次強調，「中共在每一次的每一個國際場合講的都是假話，所有退縮只是偽裝，最終目的都是想吃掉你！記住！」<br />\n<br />\n另外，中國政府有兩件事至今在所有國際場合隻字不提，一就是「文革」，二是「六四天安門事件」，文章鼓勵港人要盡力揭露中共在大陸的各種暴行，讓國際社會知道，對中共的暴行沉默，「你都會成為受害者！」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">(3) 第三顆核彈，就是要向世人展示香港人爭取自由的決心</span>，文章說，「如果有一首歌像核彈一樣，這首就是代表自由的美國國歌，香港人要爭取美國政府、人民支持，吸引美國與國際傳媒報導。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/08/24/904769.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2019%2F08%2F24%2F904769.html&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUIeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=a18ac1cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/08/24/904769.html</a>"},{"pid":"5101f87a5622429409f1fa32cd67e374a1afbe2d","tid":1503151,"uid":165997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:26:42.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"450f176d79d8976b0356da5dea0c26b6c1169475","tid":1503151,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T01:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191029fab73c58609ec7de02de141631e2ec2d81","tid":1503151,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cde06510e1252cbbb83a1f935505f8683aad838","tid":1503151,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7baab0656160d0f5174daf116042a3078afabd4f","tid":1503151,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:17:00.000Z","msg":"第二點最重要  依家國際社會仲有好多國家懵盛盛咁  以為中共係好人<br />\n其他嗰啲就為左經濟行綏靖政策<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一個文宣方向應該係對全華人  特別係對中國內部  一黎講明香港嘅示威唔係港獨  二黎要宣揚反共  分別國家同政權"},{"pid":"49d18aa14a3865698553d072e61298d6ed16a3cb","tid":1503151,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4924ffc96b6103038fe65ce89c54f3f6af20cb3","tid":1503151,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:18:21.000Z","msg":"中國威脅論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#chinazi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68cbc944d2cd969d227d20cf1ad79c6657522fde","tid":1503151,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:18:57.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n【突發文宣計劃第二期！】<br />\n請幫手推同訂閱TG"},{"pid":"c9815cc6f4c749661e2f9d3d88f03436d3b88af6","tid":1503151,"uid":35438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T02:23:37.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}